                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4002" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0338</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9918 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">欣凯医药：创业企业的危机管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cinkate Corporation: An Entrepreneurial Firm’s Crisis Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李小玲，陶奕达，吴祝欣，孟添，于晓宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学管理学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">欣凯医药</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">欣凯医药；爱若华；危机管理；反脆弱性；创业；2019百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cinkate Corporation; ‘Airohua’; Crisis management; Anti-fragility; Entrepreneurship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">欣凯医药是集新药研发、药品生产、药品销售和药品推广于一体的国际化医药集团，其核心产品是用于治疗类风湿关节炎的国家一类新药“爱若华”。为了监测“爱若华”的不良反应，欣凯医药在全国范围内开展了药品上市后的安全性观察。本案例描述了欣凯医药在开展安全性观察后遭遇日本“Arava致死”危机的全过程，讲述了欣凯医药如何应对危机、并借助“安全性观察”积累数据而实现转“危”为“机”。在数字时代，创业环境的不确定性大大加剧，危机已不再是小概率事件而是常态化事件。本案例的目的在于让学生认识到创业企业面临危机时的脆弱性以及创业企业在处理危机时都会存在失误，启发学生对创业过程中的危机管理进行深度思考，从而建立起有效的危机管理机制以应对环境的不确定性。本案例对创业企业在不确定环境中的危机管理具有重要价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Cinkate Corporation is an international pharmaceutical group that integrates the R&amp;D of new drugs, drug production, drug sales, and drug promotion. The core product of Cinkate Corporation is the national first-in-class new drug ‘Airohua’ for the treatment of rheumatoid arthritis. In order to monitor adverse reactions of ‘Airohua’, Cinkate Corporation carried out nationwide safety surveillance after the drug’s launch. The case describes the entire process of the ‘adverse reactions of Arava in Japan’ crisis after the safety surveillance, and describes how Cinkate Corporation responded to the crisis and turned the ‘crisis’ to an ‘opportunity’ with safety surveillance data. In the digital era, the entrepreneurial environment becomes more and more uncertain, and thus, crises are common in this era. This case aims to help students understand the fragility of entrepreneurial firms in crises, and their liability to cope with crises. The case inspires students’ deep thinking on crisis management in entrepreneurial process, and makes students aware of building an effective crisis management policy for entrepreneurial firms to cope with uncertainty. The case offers great insights to the crisis management of entrepreneurial firms in uncertain environment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2004</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《危机管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业机会 动态能力 核心竞争力</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
